use Laminas\Db\Adapter\Adapter;\n    use Laminas\Db\Sql\Sql;\n    \n    $adapter = new Adapter([\n        'driver'   => 'Pdo_Mysql',\n        'database' => 'mydb',\n        'username' => 'user',\n        'password' => 'password',\n        'hostname' => 'localhost',\n    ]);\n\n    $sql = new Sql($adapter);\n    $select = $sql->select();\n    $select->from('users')->where(['id' => $userId]);\n\n    $statement = $sql->prepareStatementForSqlObject($select);\n    $result = $statement->execute();